115
00:08:30,458 --> 00:08:31,958
I'M NOT A HUMAN BEING.

116
00:08:32,041 --> 00:08:33,416
I'M A DIFFERENT
KIND OF CREATURE.

117
00:08:44,833 --> 00:08:46,416
- DAMN IT.

118
00:08:46,500 --> 00:08:47,958
DAMN IT!

119
