00:10:38,625 --> 00:10:40,541
- YOU TOOK HER
AWAY FROM US.

152
00:10:40,625 --> 00:10:43,875
NOW YOU'RE THE ONLY ONE
LEFT FOR US, MAMA.

153
00:10:43,958 --> 00:10:46,833
AND YOU WANT TO RUN AWAY
ALL BY YOURSELF.

154
00:10:47,958 --> 00:10:49,875
IT'S NOT FAIR, MAMA.

155
00:10:49,958 --> 00:10:51,750
DON'T JUST GO OFF
ON YOUR OWN

156
00:10:51,833 --> 00:10:53,625
AND LOVE SOMEONE
OTHER THAN ME.

157
00:10:53,708 --> 00:10:55,375
NO ONE BUT ME.

158
