CHANGED SO MUCH, AREN'T YOU?

167
00:11:20,083 --> 00:11:21,916
- ( crying )

168
00:11:22,000 --> 00:11:23,250
- ( gun cocks )

169
00:11:23,333 --> 00:11:24,916
- TURN IT ALL BACK.

170
00:11:25,000 --> 00:11:27,208
TURN IT ALL BACK
TO THE WAY IT WAS.

171
00:11:30,333 --> 00:11:31,583
- EUREKA, DON'T.

172
00:11:39,375 --> 00:11:40,958
( gasps )

173
