LINCK, YOU'VE GROWN TALLER.

192
00:13:09,791 --> 00:13:14,375
MAETER, YOU'VE BECOME
THE BIG SISTER FOR THEM NOW.

193
00:13:14,458 --> 00:13:16,041
MAURICE,

194
00:13:16,125 --> 00:13:18,375
I WATCHED YOU THE MOST.

195
00:13:18,458 --> 00:13:20,958
