WILL BE THE STUFF
OF THE DISTANT PAST.

199
00:13:39,791 --> 00:13:41,375
BUT UNTIL THEN,

200
00:13:41,458 --> 00:13:43,416
I'LL ALWAYS
DO MY BEST FOR YOU.

201
00:13:43,500 --> 00:13:44,750
'CAUSE I LOVE YOU.

202
00:13:44,833 --> 00:13:47,416
AS MUCH AS YOUR MAMA DOES.

203
00:13:47,500 --> 00:13:50,250
AND I WANT TO TALK TO YOU
WITH A SMILE.

204
00:13:52,500 --> 00:13:54,791
AND THAT'S THE REASON WHY

205
00:13:54,875 --> 00:13:57,166
YOU SHOULDN'T BE
USING A GUN LIKE THIS.

206
00:13:57,833 --> 00:13:59,750
THAT RIGHT, MR. CHARLES?

207
