00:15:25,916 --> 00:15:27,833
IF THE MATERIAL WORLD
IS GOING TO END?

233
00:15:27,916 --> 00:15:30,208
- THE ARMY IS PLANNING
ON ANNIHILATING ALL OF

234
00:15:30,291 --> 00:15:31,916
THE SCUB CORALS
BEFORE THAT CAN HAPPEN.

235
00:15:32,000 --> 00:15:33,166
- NOT THE ARMY.

236
00:15:33,250 --> 00:15:35,166
A YOUNG MAN NAMED
DEWEY NOVAK.

237
00:15:35,250 --> 00:15:36,625
- ( gasps )

238
00:15:38,250 --> 00:15:40,166
